        <updateDate>2021-07-01T01:39:17Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Executive Branch Emissions Transparency Act</b></p> <p>This bill requires the Office of Management and Budget to establish and maintain a publicly accessible and searchable database of fossil fuel-powered travel by the President, the Vice President, and political appointees where such travel is on official business or paid for by a third party if the individual is appearing in their official capacity.</p> <p>The bill makes an exception where publishing on the database could be deemed a national security risk.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
